    "description": "The wait is finally over! <br />\r\n<br />\r\nLet’s be honest with each other, have you thought about opening your very own rug store? Or monopolizing the intergalactic rug market? Or being named Roy?? <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you have an answer to any of those questions, Roy’s Rugs is perfect for you!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSIMULATE THE MARKET<br />\r\nBuy rugs and sell them for a higher price on the rug market!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMANAGE A TEAM<br />\r\nRecruit the best sales team in the galaxy to maximise your profits!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTEST YOUR SKILLS<br />\r\nPlay with your friends and find out who is the better rugspreneur!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSCIENCE?<br />\r\nDo you even know how rugs are made? Find out now or forever live in the dark!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCONQUER THE GALAXY<br />\r\nSet up shop after shop after shop and prestige your way to godhood!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRUGS<br />\r\nIt’s all rugs!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n---------------------------------------------------------------<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHere’s what others have to say:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“Why did you make a game about rugs?” - Mother<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“This game is exactly like real life. This is how the rug market works.” - Rug Expert<br />\r\n<br />\r\n“They have effectively revolutionized the gaming industry. Truly a masterpiece that transcends what we think we know about gaming.” - Big Tech",
